{"tid":49911,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屌！公司個死肥婆柯完屎唔撚開抽氣扇","createTime":"2016-12-22T05:00:06.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-23T02:09:43.000Z","uid":51957,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"35ab33d86f0cc60e2417ca7df9f2b009a4c6b0ed","tid":49911,"uid":51957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T05:00:06.000Z","msg":"是咁的 公司有個死肥婆同事 咁佢就sales黎既，而我就坐佢對面，我每日都好撚痛苦，點解？因為佢每日同客講電話就chok到把肥聲變到懶係瘦同嬌削咁，而我因為坐正佢對面焗住要聽哂佢每日講電話既時間 真係好撚嘔心，都算<br />\n佢仲要成日返工都好鐘意著d鮮色啊 白色既鬆身衫 仲要帶個頭cool 頭cool上面仲有雞那咁大隻<span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>粉紅色</strong></span>蝴蝶結係上面 <strong>喂大佬啊</strong> 你都40到尾啦 又肥又老 塊面又搽哂厚粉同對手又完全唔撚同顏色 隻手又巢皮又剩 真係好撚核突同嘔心 好心肥婆就咪撚成日著到咁啦 好影響工作心態同環境架屌你<br />\n<br />\n好啦都算 每日返到公司一坐低左做野就對住電腦芒 可以眼不見為淨 但係呢條肥婆去完pantry沖咖啡飲 返埋位行個段路仔(10幾步左右) 屌你 個地下 <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">係 震 架 <span style=\"color: red;\">! ! !</span></span></strong> 我坐係位個陣對腳係feel到地下震架 真係唔敢想像比佢撞一下會變成點撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nOK 我離撚哂題 我知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但真係一講開呢個肥婆就覺得佢好撚黑人憎 停唔到 Ok入正題 今朝我係pantry 整野擺飯盒落雪櫃個陣 個肥婆咁岩去完廁所出黎 咁我冇為意 我就諗住去廁所柯尿 點知行到個廁所門口已經聞到陣陣屎味 之後一望 個抽氣扇掣上面粒紅燈冇著既 我就即刻著撚哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌你老未平時係公司著到成條肥肉蟲咁行黎行去都算 最多唔撚望你 但你柯屎唔開抽氣扇呢下真係 仆街以後都唔去個格廁所 硬起形住有陣肥婆屎味 之後我同其中一個同事講呢件事 佢竟然話：係啊 屌 佢慣犯黎既 成日都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  話唔記得 都唔知係咪特登唔開抽氣扇想霸左一個廁所據為己有<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過好彩 公司有兩個廁所<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但咁落去我唔知我仲可以係公司生存到幾耐 我好似每日都係到玩命咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38336aa02141bb09573fc8c6381df1bcb7fe5540","tid":49911,"uid":30694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T05:04:25.000Z","msg":"腎仔<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0vDGt.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0vDGt.gif&h=6e070bbf&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw肥婆真係好撚痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68810f3d8756401560b4c24ec4077c5dddcb5f95","tid":49911,"uid":44916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T05:30:39.000Z","msg":"以前我間公司個Sales又係chok晒聲又高音又要扮嗲，叫到成間office都聽到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37019fecae24b646f4c1782a9c9902e543f09d70","tid":49911,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T15:25:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個肥婆下次去埋另一個廁所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b89fe53de0f29efe5f8a230c088c0d05c95bab22","tid":49911,"uid":51957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T00:55:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>腎仔<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0vDGt.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0vDGt.gif&h=6e070bbf&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw肥婆真係好撚痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唉 點解每份工都有肥婆老是常出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4e7765f03c30cf5db41c5f5eec457c4bd032f9f","tid":49911,"uid":51957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T00:57:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前我間公司個Sales又係chok晒聲又高音又要扮嗲，叫到成間office都聽到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nsales就係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e57b648d0a8409633b562f3afb9fbdd72c9e1478","tid":49911,"uid":51957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T00:57:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquot